  <brief_title>Pemetrexed and Carboplatin in Locally Advanced or Metastatic Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of Alimta and Carboplatin in the Treatment of Patients With Locally Advanced or Metastatic Breast Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
