  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a nonrandomized study of pemetrexed plus carboplatin, with the primary objective of
      determining the efficacy of the combination in tumor reduction, in patients with locally
      advanced or metastatic breast cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
